            "name": "Lightning Blast",
            "requirement": "The stormdrinker is quickened due to Absorb Shock; Effect The stormdrinker dismisses its Absorb Shock benefits to expel lightning in a 60-foot line, dealing 8d6 electricity damage (DC 25 basic Reflex save).",
